flowchart TD
  A["INPUT: devices_list"] --> B["PLAY 1: Build Dynamic Inventory
(add_host → cmdb_devices)"]

  B --> C["PLAY 2: For each host in cmdb_devices
(loop)"]

  C --> D["Retrieve CI from ServiceNow
Search by inventory_hostname
+ detect empty fields"]

  D --> E{"CI exists?"}
  E -->|Yes| F["mode = enforced"]
  E -->|No| G["mode = default"]

  D --> H{"device.mode defined?"}
  H -->|Yes| I["mode = device.mode"]

  F --> J
  G --> J
  I --> J

  J["Select template by device_type
(f5 / f5lb / fortigate / paloalto)"] --> K["Render Jinja2 template
• enforced_vars always
• default_vars by mode
• manual_template if defined"]

  K --> L["Prepare update_cmdb_ci vars
(create=true if CI missing)"]

  L --> M["Call tte.common.update_cmdb_ci"]

  M --> N["CI created/updated
→ next host"]

  N --> C
